- Melee
-- Staggers/knocks back targets on hit
- Gand Shock Staff
-- Based on Lightsaber
-- Yellow/Staff styles
-- Saber Defense (1)
-- Blaster Deflect (1)
-- 30% less damage
-- 33/16% shorter reach
-- 33% wider radius
-- Can block blasters/sabers
- W-90 Concussion Rifle
-- Based on T-21 (1)
-- 75% more FP damage

^8Attributes:
- Stamina (3)
- Dexterity (3)
- Healing (2)
- Shield Recharge (1)
- Findsman Precognition (Passive Force Sense 1)
- Mind Trick Immunity (2)
- Force Block (3)
- BP-free jumps

^3Abilities:
- Sprint [CS1]
- Dexterity Roll [CS2]
- Dodge (3) [CS3]

An infamous bounty hunter and Gand Findsman with uncanny tracking abilities that could be considered a sixth sense. He often took bounties alongside 4-LOM."